title: Fantasy Draft Redo + TNF Preview, Buy or Sell - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/13
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode as we enter Week 6! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason take turns picking the top 24 players for rest of season! Which players have made the elite tier jump over the first five weeks? Plus, the Week 6 edition of Buy or Sell, and a preview of the Thursday Night Football matchup between the Buccaneers and Eagles. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 13th, 2021.
  
 (05:25) - Buy or Sell
 (13:30) - NFL News
 (17:20) - Fantasy Draft Redo
 (53:55) - Thursday Night Preview - Buccaneers at Eagles
